HEADWORD: Forbiddance
<hw>For*bid"dance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
forbidding; prohibition; command or edict against a thing.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How hast thou yield to transgress⟦br⟧
The strict <qex>forbiddance</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forbidden</ent>⟦br⟧
